    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Before you start cooking, take your<strong> chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Combine your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(cant't handle the heat? Go easy), <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> in a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>– this is your<strong> marinade</strong></p>",
